==一氧化氮对其他生物的影响==
===植物===
一氧化氮在植物中有以下四种生成途径：L-精氨酸依赖性一氧化氮合酶<ref>{{cite journal|title=Cellular and subcellular localization of endogenous nitric oxide in young and senescent pea plants|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_plant-physiology_2004-09_136_1/page/2722|author=Corpas, F. J. |journal=Plant Physiology|volume=136 |issue=1 |pages=2722–33 |year=2004|doi=10.1104/pp.104.042812|pmid=15347796|pmc=523336|first2=JB|last3=Carreras |first3=A|last4=Quirós |first4=M|last5=León |first5=AM|last6=Romero-Puertas |first6=MC|last7=Esteban |first7=FJ|last8=Valderrama |first8=R|last9=Palma |first9=JM|last10=Sandalio |first10=LM|last11=Gómez |first11=M|last12=Del Río |first12=LA|last2=Barroso }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Corpas, F. J. |title=Constitutive arginine-dependent nitric oxide synthase activity in different organs of pea seedlings during plant development|journal=Planta|volume=224|issue=2 |pages=246–54|year=2006|doi=10.1007/s00425-005-0205-9 |pmid=16397797 |first2=Juan B. |last3=Carreras|first3=Alfonso |last4=Valderrama|first4=Raquel |last5=Palma|first5=José M. |last6=León|first6=Ana M. |last7=Sandalio|first7=Luisa M. |last8=Del Río|first8=Luis A|last2=Barroso}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |author=Valderrama, R.|title=Nitrosative stress in plants|journal=FEBS Lett|volume=581|issue=3 |pages=453–61|year=2007|doi=10.1016/j.febslet.2007.01.006 |pmid=17240373 |first2=Francisco J. |last3=Carreras|first3=Alfonso |last4=Fernández-Ocaña|first4=Ana |last5=Chaki|first5=Mounira |last6=Luque|first6=Francisco |last7=Gómez-Rodríguez|first7=María V. |last8=Colmenero-Varea|first8=Pilar |last9=Del Río|first9=Luis A. |last10=Barroso|first10=Juan B.|last2=Corpas}}</ref>（植物中是否存在动物NOS同源物存在争议）<ref>{{cite journal |author=Corpas, F. J.|title=Enzymatic sources of nitric oxide in plant cells – beyond one protein–one function|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_new-phytologist_2004-05_162_2/page/246|journal=New Phytologist|volume=162|issue= 2|pages=246–7|year=2004|doi=10.1111/j.1469-8137.2004.01058.x |last2=Barroso |first2=Juan B. |last3=Del Rio |first3=Luis A.}}</ref>，质膜结合[[硝酸盐还原酶|硝酸盐还原酶]]，[[线粒体|线粒体]][[电子传递链|电子传递链]]以及非酶促反应。一氧化氮在植物中作为一种信号分子，主要在抗[[氧化应激|氧化应激]]和[[植物病理学|植物病理学]]作用等方面起效。研究表明，使用一氧化氮处理切花可以保鲜。<ref>{{Cite journal | last1 = Siegel-Itzkovich | first1 = J. | title = Viagra makes flowers stand up straight | doi = 10.1136/bmj.319.7205.274a | journal = BMJ | volume = 319 | issue = 7205 | pages = 274 | year = 1999 | pmid = 10426722| pmc =1126920 }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | last1 = Mur | first1 = L. A. | last2 = Mandon | first2 = J. | last3 = Persijn | first3 = S. | last4 = Cristescu | first4 = S. M. | last5 = Moshkov | first5 = I. E. | last6 = Novikova | first6 = G. V. | last7 = Gupta | first7 = K. J. | year = 2013 | title = Nitric oxide in plants: an assessment of the current state of knowledge | journal = [[AoB_PLANTS|AoB PLANTS]] | volume =  5| page =  pls052| doi = 10.1093/aobpla/pls052 | pmid = 23372921 | pmc = 3560241 }}</ref>一氧化氮可以调节某些植物病理学和生理学作用，如植物过敏反应，共生作用（如豆科植物与[[根瘤菌|根瘤菌]]共生产生根瘤），[[侧根|侧根]]、[[不定根|不定根]]、[[根毛|根毛]]的发育，[[气孔|气孔]]的开合等。一氧化氮常在[[细胞器|细胞器]]内产生，诸如[[线粒体|线粒体]]、[[过氧化物酶体|过氧化物酶体]]和[[叶绿体|叶绿体]]都能产生一氧化氮，使之参与到与活性氧发生的抗氧化反应中去。<ref>Verma, K., Mehta, S. K., & Shekhawat, G. S. (2013). Nitric oxide (NO) counteracts cadmium induced cytotoxic processes mediated by reactive oxygen species (ROS) in Brassica juncea: cross-talk between ROS, NO and antioxidant responses. ''[[BioMetals_(journal)|BioMetals]]'': an international journal on the role of metal ions in biology, biochemistry, and medicine.</ref>一氧化氮指标可用于N端[[蛋白酶解|蛋白质降解]]、非生物胁迫应激（旱涝、盐碱胁迫）的表征。<ref name="Nitric oxide sensing in plants is m">{{cite journal |last1=Gibbs |first1=DJ |last2=Md Isa |first2=N |last3=Movahedi |first3=M |last4=Lozano-Juste |first4=J |last5=Mendiondo |first5=GM |last6=Berckhan |first6=S |last7=Marín-de la Rosa |first7=N |last8=Vicente Conde |first8=J |last9=Sousa Correia |first9=C |last10=Pearce |first10=SP |last11=Bassel |first11=GW |last12=Hamali |first12=B |last13=Talloji |first13=P |last14=Tomé |first14=DF 