 }}</ref>大气[[氮循环|氮循环]]过程中的一氧化氮可通过气孔进入到[[维管植物|维管植物]]中，对叶片瘢痕的产生、植物固氮、组织[[坏死|坏死]]产生影响。<ref>C.Michael Hogan. 2010. [http://www.eoearth.org/article/Abiotic_factor?topic=49461 "Abiotic factor"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.eoearth.org/article/Abiotic_factor?topic=49461 |date=20130608071757 }}. ''[[Encyclopedia_of_Earth|Encyclopedia of Earth]]''. eds Emily Monosson and C. Cleveland. [[National_Council_for_Science_and_the_Environment|National Council for Science and the Environment]]. Washington DC</ref>

