===细菌===
[[File:Deinococcus_radiodurans.jpg|thumb]]]]
通常一氧化氮抑制细菌生长，并作为一种特性运用于免疫反应中。但是某些情况下一氧化氮可以保护细菌。2009年一报道显示，[[抗辐射奇异球菌|抗辐射奇异球菌]]在经过紫外线辐射损伤后，一个增加一氧化氮表达的基因启动，促进了DNA修复与细胞生长；而在该基因敲除的情况下，细菌仅能修复DNA而无法生长。<ref>{{cite journal|title=Endogenous nitric oxide regulates the recovery of the radiation-resistant bacterium Deinococcus radiodurans from exposure to UV light|author=Bhumit A. Patel |author2=Magali Moreau |author3=Joanne Widom |author4=Huan Chen |author5=Longfei Yin |author6=Yuejin Hua |author7=Brian R. Crane|journal=PNAS|year=2009|volume=106|issue=43|pages=18183–18188|doi=10.1073/pnas.0907262106|pmid=19841256|pmc=2775278|bibcode=2009PNAS..10618183P }}</ref>

